<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\stdio\putc">putc</sample>
    <title> putc, putwc </title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> stio_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>将字符写入流。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>putc</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>c</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>待写入的字符</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>FILE*</param_type>
                <param_name>stream</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>指向文件结构的指针</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>wint_t</return_val>
        <func_name>putwc</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>wint_t</param_type>
                <param_name>c</param_name>
            </func_param>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>FILE*</param_type>
                <param_name>stream</param_name>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>返回写入的字符；如果出错或已到文件尾，putc返回EOF，putwc返回WEOF。可以通过函数<link url="ferror.htm">ferror</link>或<link url="feof.htm">feofr</link>检验是发生错误还是已到文件尾。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>putc将单一字符c写入流的当前位置，并将当前位置移到下一位置；任何整型值都可以传递给putc，但只有低8位会被写入流。如果发生读错误，将设置流的错误指示器。putwc是putc的宽字符版本。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>putc</routine_name>
            <headerfile>stdio.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>putwc</routine_name>
            <headerfile>stdio.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2004,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* putc.cpp: This program uses putc to write buffer
 * to a stream. If an error occurs, the program
 * stops before writing the entire buffer.
 */

#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;

int main()
{
    FILE *stream;
    char *p, buffer[] = &quot;This is the line of output\n&quot;;
    int  ch;

    ch = 0;
    /* Make standard out the stream and write to it. */
    stream = stdout;
    for (p = buffer; (ch != EOF) &amp;&amp; (*p != &apos;\0&apos;); p++)
        ch = putc(*p, stream);
    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
This is the line of output
</result>

   

